24
00:01:57.737 --> 00:02:09.575
Observation. one side of the large square is made of two segments. 2026 and 2025. so the side length of the large square is 2026 plus 2025

25
00:02:09.575 --> 00:02:12.612
Therefore. the area of the large square is

26
00:02:12.612 --> 00:02:18.137
Open parenthesis 2026 plus 2025 close parenthesis squared

27
00:02:18.137 --> 00:02:21.387
And all the pieces in the figure together represent

28
00:02:21.387 --> 00:02:23.012
2a minus 1

29
00:02:23.012 --> 00:02:24.137
So we have

30
00:02:24.137 --> 00:02:31.300
2a minus 1 equals open parenthesis 2026 plus 2025 close parenthesis squared

31
00:02:31.300 --> 00:02:33.775
Taking the square root of both sides

32
00:02:33.775 --> 00:02:48.500
The square root of 2a minus 1 equals the square root of open parenthesis 2026 plus 2025 close parenthesis squared. equal to 2026 plus 2025. equal to 4051

33
00:02:48.500 --> 00:02:51.000
Answer. 4051

